  <description>
    <p>
      Take your links anywhere and keep them fresh! Frigoligo is a wallabag client striving to be simple but also fast and easy to use. Just like wallabag, Frigoligo is free to use, ad-free and open source.
    </p>
    <p>
      You need a wallabag instance to use this application.
    </p>
  </description>
  
